<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-01-11T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-01-11T18:00:00-05:00" n="221" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d221">
                    <note rend="inline" type="source">852.48/1408: Telegram</note>
                    <head>
                        <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Hayes</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                        </hi>
                    </head>
                    <opener>
                        <dateline rendition="#right">
                            <placeName>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-01-12T00:00:00+01:00">January 12,
                                1943—midnight</date>.<lb/>[Received January 13—8:21 a.m.]</dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>75. It would be helpful to me if you would let me know if you are agreeable
                        to calling Cardenas in and talking to him in the sense of my 17, January 4,
                        10 a.m. I am delaying further representation here pending information
                        concerning your conversation in the event you concur.</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hayes</hi>
                        </signed>
                    </closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>